{"tid":752464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國擬盡快派航母「伊莉莎白女王號」部署到太平洋地區 偕澳洲巡南海","createTime":"2018-07-22T23:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T02:35:35.000Z","uid":35790,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"05fcfc8d6d6b89f3eec3bdf6c83d5eb0f4aac58e","tid":752464,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T23:36:00.000Z","msg":"英擬派航母偕澳洲巡南海<br />\n<br />\n英澳兩國上周五在愛丁堡舉行的四部長高級座談會上宣布，兩國將聯合在中國南海舉行南海巡航行動。會議認為，中國在南海島礁不斷加強「軍事化」，使這片水域成為澳洲周邊最具威脅的地方，英國更稱會盡快將航母「伊利沙伯女王」號部署到太平洋地區，與澳洲軍艦維護南海自由航行的權利。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180723/s00013/1532283822116\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180723%2Fs00013%2F1532283822116&d=36Rt6SDeh3uDv2hevI%2BaVzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=6f000486\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180723%2Fs00013%2F1532283822116&h=068d75d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180723/s00013/1532283822116</a>"},{"pid":"1492433f344ba8edafe43904b4646685df056fac","tid":752464,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T23:37:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6add6c107d0e66ae37f239f032bed9dc4ccda3","tid":752464,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T23:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a8fda995dd3662d8bac69856952781d60185a3","tid":752464,"uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T23:42:11.000Z","msg":"不過，伊莉莎白女王號因向美採購的艦載機F-35B尚未交付，目前是一艘沒有戰機的航母。<span style=\"color: red;\">但英、美曾經達成協議，美軍陸戰隊的F-35B可以部署在伊莉莎白女王號，進行飛行和戰術訓練。</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/focus/paper/1218557\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffoc